Package: dynwrap
Type: Package
Title: Representing and Inferring Single-Cell Trajectories
Description: Provides functionality to infer trajectories from
        single-cell data, represent them into a common format, and
        adapt them. Other biological information can also be added,
        such as cellular grouping, RNA velocity and annotation. Saelens
        et al. (2019) <doi:10.1038/s41587-019-0071-9>.
